\c 149 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 149\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Faarfannaa Galataa
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Faarfannaa haaraadhaan Waaqayyoon faarfadhaa! Walga'ii warra isaaf of kennanii keessatti jajuu isaa dhageessisaa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Israa'el isa isa uumetti haa gammadu, ijoolleen Xiyoon mootii isaaniitti gammaduu isaanii haa mul'isan!
\m \bd 3\bd* Sirbanii maqaa isaa haa jajatan, dibbee fi kiraara rukutuudhaanis isa haa faarfatan.
\m \bd 4\bd* Waaqayyo saba isaatti in gammada, warra gad deebi'aniifis mo'icha kennuudhaan ulfina in argachiisa.
\m \bd 5\bd* Warri isaaf of kennan ulfina kanatti haa gammadan, afata isaanii irrattis guddisanii haa faarfatan.
\m \bd 6\bd* Waaqayyoon jajatanii ol himuun afaan isaanii keessaa, billaan gar lamaan qaramaanis harka isaanii keessaa hin bu'in!
\m \bd 7\bd* Saba lafa irraa irratti ijaa ba'uudhaaf, saba warra kaanis adabuudhaaf \bd 8\bd* mootota isaanii fuuncaadhaan, ulfina-qaboota isaaniis funyoo sibiilaatiin hidhuudhaaf, 
\m \bd 9\bd* firdii caafamee jiru isaan irratti in raawwata, kun warra isaaf of kennan hundumaaf ulfina! Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
